title: BommelZ
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, American, International, Thai, Western, Fast food, Take-out
description: A vegetarian/vegan bistro serves in-house-made food such as the voner with soy boil, veggie burger, stuffed burrito with beans or veggie dog. Vegan crepes are available. Serves fair trade coffee. Comfortable lounge atmosphere. Wi-fi. Dog friendly; one on property.
